name: colored eyelashes/非黑色的睫毛/带颜色的睫毛
description:
随便练的,别骂

睫毛颜色可与发色不同,如:白色头发与金色睫毛

white hair, (colored eyelashes, yellow eyelashes:1.2)

权重与颜色可自己控制

由于数据集处理和过拟合的原因，不加其他附加词会造成出贴脸图，建议加上视角词诸如：

upper body

Eyelash color can be different from hair color, such as:

white hair, (colored eyelashes, yellow eyelashes:1.2)

The weight and color can be controlled by yourself

And I suggest adding lens prompt, for example

upper body
